    </p>
    <p>
      To create their best work, I believe designers need psychological safety
      that can only come from mutual trust. I aim to foster that environment in
      the teams I help lead.
    </p>
    <h2 class="hidden">Values and practices</h2>
    <ul class="values-and-practices">
      {
        valuesAndPractices.map(({ value, practice }) => (
          <li>
            <span class="value">
              {value}
              <span aria-label="through" class="through" />
            </span>
            {practice}
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ul>

    <p>
      <span class="glitter"><Sparkles /></span>
      Currently looking for my next opportunity. Previously Design Manager at Clerk
      and PlanetScale; Designer at GitHub, Vox Media, and ad agencies.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="/contact">Let me know</a> if you‚Äôd like to make some magic together.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.125em;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: var(--font-family-sans);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacer));
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    @media (min-width: 590px) {
      line-height: 130%;
    }

    span {
      font-size: 0.94em;
      display: block;
      font-family: var(--font-family-serif);
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0;
    }
  }

  .glitter {
    @apply block mb-2 mt-6 md:mt-0;
    svg {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      fill: var(--color-primary);
    }
  }

  .values-and-practices {
    list-style: none;

    li {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      @media all and (max-width: 680px) {
        margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacer) * 2);
      }
      @media all and (min-width: 680px) {
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
      }
      &:nth-of-type(even) .through {
        transform: scaleY(-1);
      }
    }

    .value {
      display: flex;
      font-family: var(--font-family-sans);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 93.75%;
      @media all and (max-width: 680px) {
        margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacer) * 0.5);
      }
      @media all and (min-width: 680px) {
        justify-content: space-between;
        width: 45%;
        padding-right: var(--spacer);
      }
    }

    .through {
      @media all and (min-width: 680px) {
        margin-left: var(--spacer);
        flex: 1;
        background: url("data:image/svg+xml;base64,")
          center right no-repeat;
        background-size: auto 1em;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
